CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 16, 1958, pg. B7, reads: "Aqua Show Participants - Pictured are members of the Sidney Wilson Dance Group who participated in the Ammon Center Aqua Show, Aug. 8.  Left to right: Delores Williams, John Sullivan, Carmen Wilson, Joanne Neal, Sidney Wilson and Brenda McCollum. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of Sidney Wilson Dance Group, from left: Delores Williams, John Sullivan, Carmen Wilson, Joanne Neal, Sidney Wilson and Brenda McCollum, posed at Ammon Center
